nodes.text: At some point during the Galactic Civil War, a humanoid male Dark Jedi used the Force to drain life-force from a Human male. With flowing black hair and red eyes, the humanoid had white skin with burgundy-striped patterns on his face. The Dark Jedi wore black and red armor while attacking the Human.

The Dark Jedi was pictured on the card "Force Drain" from the Agents of Deception expansion set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game. The set was released in 2009, and the Dark Jedi was drawn by Kieran Yanner.
